OL,3,CSouthport Inquiry: What is it and what
OL,4,Cwill it hear?
OL,6,FThe Southport Inquiry has been
OL,7,Festablished to "thoroughly
OL,8,Finvestigate" the circumstances around
OL,9,Fthe deaths of three girls who were
OL,10,Fkilled in a knife attack as they
OL,11,Fattended a dance class.
OL,13,FBebe King, six, Elsie Dot Stancombe,
OL,14,Fseven, and Alice Da Silva Aguiar nine,
OL,15,Fwere murdered at a Taylor Swift-themed
OL,16,Fdance club in Southport on 29 July
OL,17,F2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/15
