OL,3,CSouthport Inquiry: What is it and what
OL,4,Cwill it hear?
OL,6,FThree separate referrals were made to
OL,7,Fthe Government's counter-terror
OL,8,Fprogramme Prevent about the attacker's
OL,9,Fbehaviour in the years before the
OL,10,Fattack, as well as six separate calls
OL,11,Fto police.
OL,13,FThe inquiry, which will have legal
OL,14,Fpowers to receive evidence and hear
OL,15,Fwitness testimony, was formally
OL,16,Flaunched on Monday, 7 April.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/15
