OL,3,CSouthport Inquiry: What is it and what
OL,4,Cwill it hear?
OL,6,FThe first phase will have particular
OL,7,Ffocus on issues around policing, the
OL,8,Fcriminal justice system and the
OL,9,Fmultiple agencies involved with the 18-
OL,10,Fyear-old before the attack.
OL,12,FThe second phase will examine the
OL,13,Fwider issue of young people being
OL,14,Fdrawn into extreme violence.
OL,16,FWhen and where will the inquiry begin?
