OL,3,CSouthport Inquiry: What is it and what
OL,4,Cwill it hear?
OL,6,FThe Government announced the inquiry
OL,7,Fin January after the perpetrator was
OL,8,Fsentenced for murdering the three
OL,9,Fgirls and attempting to murder 10
OL,10,Fothers.
OL,12,FIt will be held at Liverpool Town
OL,13,FHall, will begin on 8 July for two
OL,14,Fdays of evidence, before breaking for
OL,15,Fthe summer and reconvening in
OL,16,FSeptember.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/15
