OL,3,CSouthport Inquiry: What is it and what
OL,4,Cwill it hear?
OL,6,FIt will begin at 2pm with an opening
OL,7,Fstatement from the inquiry chair Sir
OL,8,FAdrian Fulford. Evidence from four
OL,9,Ffamilies whose children were injured
OL,10,Fin the knife attacks will be heard the
OL,11,Ffollowing day.
OL,13,FWhat will phase one of the inquiry
OL,14,Flook at?
OL,16,FBroadly, phase one will look into what
OL,17,Fcould have been done to prevent the
OL,18,Fmurders.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/15
