OL,3,CSouthport Inquiry: What is it and what
OL,4,Cwill it hear?
OL,6,FThe official terms of reference for
OL,7,Fthe inquiry states it will look to
OL,8,F"establish a definitive account of the
OL,9,Fevents leading up to the Southport
OL,10,Fattack and the attack itself".
OL,12,FThis account will include the facts
OL,13,Fand circumstances of each of the
OL,14,Fgirl's deaths as well as the accounts
OL,15,Fof those directly impacted by the
OL,16,Fattack.
OL,18,FWhat will it look at specifically
OL,19,Frelated to the perpetrator?
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/15
