OL,3,CSouthport Inquiry: What is it and what
OL,4,Cwill it hear?
OL,6,FPhase one will look at an overall
OL,7,Ftimeline of perpetrator's history and
OL,8,Finteractions with various state
OL,9,Fsystems including criminal justice,
OL,10,Feducation, social care and healthcare.
OL,12,FIt will review the decision-making and
OL,13,Finformation-sharing by local services
OL,14,Fand agencies which interacted with the
OL,15,Fkiller before the attack to see if
OL,16,Fthere were opportunities to manage the
OL,17,Frisk he posed to the public.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/15
