OL,3,CSouthport Inquiry: What is it and what
OL,4,Cwill it hear?
OL,6,FA review into the Prevent referrals
OL,7,Fpublished in February found there was
OL,8,Fsufficient risk posed by the teenager
OL,9,Fto keep his cases within Prevent
OL,10,Factive, but these were closed
OL,11,Fprematurely while too much focus was
OL,12,Fplaced on a lack of distinct ideology.
OL,14,FThe inquiry will draw on evidence from
OL,15,Finterviews with witnesses and
OL,16,Fdisclosure from 15 organisations,
OL,17,Fincluding MI5, Counter-Terrorism
OL,18,FPolicing, NHS England and Merseyside
OL,19,FPolice.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/15
