OL,3,CSouthport Inquiry: What is it and what
OL,4,Cwill it hear?
OL,6,FIt will make any required
OL,7,Frecommendations for improvements.
OL,9,FWhat will phase two look like?
OL,11,FPhase two will examine the wider issue
OL,12,Fof young people being drawn into
OL,13,Fextreme violence but, the government
OL,14,Fsaid, the findings of phase one will
OL,15,Finfluence the focus of phase two.
