OL,3,CSouthport Inquiry: What is it and what
OL,4,Cwill it hear?
OL,6,FIt is expected to consider "the
OL,7,Fadequacy of multi-agency systems to
OL,8,Faddress the risk posed by young people
OL,9,Fwhose fixation or obsession with, and
OL,10,Fdesire to commit, acts of extreme
OL,11,Fviolence presents a significant risk
OL,12,Fto public safety".
OL,14,FWho is charing the inquiry?
OL,16,FSir Adrian Fulford is chairing the
OL,17,Finquiry.
