OL,3,CSouthport Inquiry: What is it and what
OL,4,Cwill it hear?
OL,6,FHe is a former vice-president of the
OL,7,FCourt of Appeal who sentenced Sarah
OL,8,FEverard's killer Wayne Couzens to a
OL,9,Fwhole-life term.
OL,11,FAnnouncing his role, Home Secretary
OL,12,FYvette Cooper said: "Sir Adrian
OL,13,FFulford will bring a wealth of legal
OL,14,Fand criminal justice expertise to this
OL,15,Frole, and I am pleased he has agreed
OL,16,Fto chair the inquiry."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/15
