OL,3,CSouthport Inquiry: What is it and what
OL,4,Cwill it hear?
OL,6,FIt is believed he has already met with
OL,7,Fthe bereaved families as they have
OL,8,Fsaid they wanted to help shape the
OL,9,Finquiry's approach and ensure the
OL,10,Fvoices of all the victims are heard.
OL,12,FWhy was the inquiry established?
OL,14,FThe home secretary said she hoped the
OL,15,Fpublic inquiry would "provide insights
OL,16,Finto any failings that allowed a young
OL,17,Fman with a previous history of
OL,18,Fviolence to commit this horrendous
OL,19,Fattack".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/15
