OL,3,CSouthport Inquiry: What is it and what
OL,4,Cwill it hear?
OL,6,FShe added: "The brutal murder of three
OL,7,Fyoung girls: Bebe, Elsie and Alice in
OL,8,FSouthport was an unimaginable tragedy
OL,9,F` we owe it to their families, and all
OL,10,Fthose affected on that terrible day to
OL,11,Fquickly understand what went wrong,
OL,12,Fanswer difficult questions and do
OL,13,Feverything in our power to prevent
OL,14,Fsomething like this from happening
OL,15,Fagain."
OL,17,FHow will the conclusions of the
OL,18,Finquiry be given?
